metadata.name: FATHER
metadata.description:
Chaos is the beginning.
There is no light in it, and where there is no light, there is eternal darkness.
Chaos has no beginning and no end.
He is the monolith of the world.
Father was never born and exists outside of time.
The Son is the offspring of the Chaos and its consequences.
An UnHoly Spirit is an eternity without time, enveloping the invisible world.
Chaos controls all the processes of the world through the Son within the eternal realm of the UnHoly Spirit.
And here, through the infinity of the uncreated, worlds and stars are created.
Chaos is the order and the ruler of the worlds, which people will never be able to understand.
This is the true order and basis of everything.
All this was created by the invisible hand of the Son of Chaos under the auspices of the Father.
The UnHoly Spirit is everywhere and always, never and nowhere.
Beyond space and time.

Mix AI + pure math fractals + After Effects

Animation 2500x2500
